orced to sit on my arse watching a blue bar go up, so that I can do more spell damage. BUT WARRIORS OUTDMG'ed me!! Why play a necro? I should just start a warrior now, since I'm not wanted in groups cause everyone knows a warrior outdmg's me easily, and he offers more to the group, like tanking.</P><P>Please nerf warriors or else i'm quitting to play Fingerbang Online.</i></P><P><font size=1>Super Saigon Potuku defeats Abashibuu!!</font id=size1><BR><img src="http://necro.eqclasses.com/potus/abashibuu.jpg" border=0><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
